title: Northern Lights
lyrics:
Take me to the edge
I start to breathe
So caught in my head
I’m in too deep
I close my eyes

Don’t have to fight

I come out here

No need to hide



Wanna be wanna see

Wanna free what's in my mind

Moving in slow motion

All the time

Wanna be, wandering

Underneath under the northern lights

I hear it calling



I move with the wind

Flows in my veins

Stronger now within

Lost in in this space



I close my eyes

Don’t have to fight

I come out here

No need to hide



Wanna be, wanna see

Wanna free what's in my mind

Moving in slow motion

All the time

Wanna be wandering

Underneath under the northern lights

I hear it calling
